Package java111.project5

Class Order

  • java.lang.Object
    • java111.project5.Order
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    OnlineOrder
    public class Order
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is for the 'Order' superclass. An order contains customer information and information for a single product type aswell as a quantity of products. Orders in this class are NOT shipped unless they are in the 'OnlineOrder' subclass.
